In summary, the presented data show that the Al 20 Cr 10 Nb 15 Ti 20 -V 25 Zr 10 RHEA can be considered as in situ composite consisting of the soft B2 and hard C14 Laves phases mixture (Fig.  1 ). After annealing, the alloy had some plastic ductility at 22 °C and high specific strength at 800 °C (Fig.  3 ).
